Package: notebookExplorer
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - Jupyter and Quarto What-If Risk Explorer
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that backs a Quarto (R)
    notebook for interactive "what-if" exploration of risk outputs.  The
    package is intentionally small: it exposes the five client operations
    the notebook cells call.  Distributed as an example; not a validated
    clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.5.0),
    knitr (>= 1.46)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
